Package suncertify.nw

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ServerService
    This class provides a common interface for various entities on the network server.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Command
    This class defines the structure of commands to be used in all communications between the network client and network server.
    DatabaseServer
    This class represents the database server.
    GetRecordsCommand
    This class represents the command to fetch records from a network server that matches a given criteria.
    ModelNetworkImpl
    This class provides an implementation of data model to be used when accessing data from a remote data source.
    NetworkClient
    This class represents a network client.
    NetworkServer
    This class represents the network server.
    NotifyCommand
    This class represents server notifications to clients.
    ServerThread
    This class represents a server thread which encapsulates the interaction of the server with a particular client.
    ServerThreadPoolManager
    This class represents the server thread pool manager.
    UpdateRecordsCommand
    Network command to update a list of records.
